title: Yetisports v1.0.0 [PD]
description:
The original is back! Yeti can now kick the penguin even further. We have completely reworked this classic game. What can you look forward to? 

3D comic-style graphics, a classic mode, along with 8 extended levels, global high score lists and lots more. If you missed out on the original, which was downloaded over 300 million times, now is the perfect time for you to try it for yourself!

Have fun and "let me flyyyyyyy!"

THIS IS WHAT YOU DO:

- Tap or click once to jump off.
- Tap or click again to swing yeti's club.
- Time this for best speed and hit angle.
- To control the Pingu once in fligt, tilt your device or use the Left/Right arrow keys
- The Pingu is aligned optimally, when aircushions begin to appear below his body
- Tap or click while in flight to flap you wings and gain some height

THIS IS WHAT YOU GET:

- the most popular part of the YETISPORTS series
- gorgeous 3D background graphics
- global online highscores
